msgid ""
"The <abbr title=\"Maximum Transmission Unit\">MTU</abbr> to be published in "
"<abbr title=\"Router Advertisement, ICMPv6 Type 134\">RA</abbr> messages. "
"Minimum is 1280 bytes."
